; XC Scoreboard Results Script
; Send timing results to TCP port 5555 in JSON format
; Save to C:\Lynx\ and select in FinishLynx Scoreboard Options
;
; Configuration in FinishLynx:
; - Script: xc-scoreboard-results.lss
; - Serial Port: Network (Connect)
; - IP Address: 127.0.0.1 (or your server IP)
; - Port: 5555
; - Results: Auto
; - Size/Max: 335 (for large XC fields)

;;Initialization
; Empty - no initialization needed

;;ResultsHeader
; Empty - send results individually

;;Result
; Send each result as JSON on a single line
; Format: {"T":"timestamp","D":{fields}}
\00{"T":"\06%s","D":{"BIB":"\03%s","P":"\01%s","FN":"\04%s","LN":"\04%s","AF":"\05%s","T":"\06%s","CS":"\08%s","L2G":"\0a%s","EN":"","R":"","H":""}}\0d\0a

;;ResultsTrailer
; Empty - no trailer needed
